ActThe Lake of the Woods Control Board Act
PrecisAppointment of SYED M.A. MOIN of Burlington, Ontario, who is a duly qualified engineer of the Water Issues Division, Meteorological Services of Canada, Ontario Region, Department of the Environment, as the Canadian representative on the International Lake of the Woods Control Board and as a member on the Lake of the Woods Control Board, to hold office during pleasure, in the place of Dale R. Kimmett.
